      "widgets_values": [
        "BLUNT Fill path:\n\u2022 BLUNT is the local image-to-splat backend here\n\u2022 The baseline workflow uses BLUNT's da2 engine so it works without Depth Anything 3\n\u2022 BLUNT normalization is OFF by default so the initial viewer camera stays closer to the source view\n\u2022 Flux Fill edits only the masked regions of the reposed render\n\nIf you install Depth Anything 3, switch Load BLUNT Model to da3 for better depth quality."
      ],
      "_meta": {
        "title": "How It Works"
      },
      "color": "#332",
      "bgcolor": "#553"
    },
